text: Oswald Julen (15 February 1912 - December 1998) was a Swiss skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Swiss male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Switzerland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Zermatt
